Description_lang: |cFFFFFFFFWinning Streak!|r causes Frost Strike and Glacial Advance to have a $s2% chance to cast Frostscythe per stack at $s1% effectiveness. Losing |cFFFFFFFFWinning Streak!|r sends you into a Murderous Frenzy, casting Frostscythe at $s3% effectiveness and gaining ${$1222698s1*$mastery}% Mastery for $1222698d. Additionally, Frostscythe deals $s4% more damage to the first target struck.
